6154→        // The shell handler uses `${HOME:-/root}/.local/bin`; the Rust
6155→        // `resolve_dcg_binary` probe must fall back to the same `/root`
6156→        // when HOME is unset, otherwise the startup log could claim the
6157→        // guard is INACTIVE while the handler still resolves dcg via
